Privacy Policy

We take your privacy seriously. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and share your personal information when you use our app.

Information We Collect

When you use our app, we may collect the following information:

User input: We collect the messages you send to the chatbot within the app.

Device information: We may collect information about the device you use to access our app, such as your device's operating system, browser type, and IP address.

How We Use Your Information

We may use your information to:

Improve our app: We may use your messages to train and improve our chatbot's responses.

Personalize your experience: We may use your messages to personalize your experience within the app.

Analyze usage: We may use device information to analyze usage of our app, such as which features are most popular.

Sharing Your Information

We will not share your personal information with third parties, except in the following circumstances:

With your consent: We may share your information with third parties if you give us your consent to do so.

For legal reasons: We may share your information with third parties if we believe it is necessary to comply with a legal obligation or protect our rights.

Data Retention

We will retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide you with our app and fulfill the purposes described in this privacy policy. We may also retain and use your information as necessary to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will provide notice of any material changes to this privacy policy by posting a notice on our website or through other means.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at adnanashraf.9011@gmail.com.
